    <p class="lede">Fulgor Milano is Meneghetti S.p.A.'s Italian premium appliance brand — specialty Italian-design positioning in the US ultra-premium kitchen market, distributed through Fulgor USA. Fulgor Milano's 24-inch built-in dishwashers ship to design-forward custom kitchens where Italian-specialty positioning matters. Our LA service concentrates in design-conscious eastside (Silver Lake, Los Feliz, Highland Park), Westside design-premium (Mar Vista, Brentwood), Hollywood Hills architectural custom kitchens, and scattered Pasadena + OC luxury. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
