    <p>Service geography concentrates in design-conscious eastside neighborhoods (Silver Lake, Los Feliz, Highland Park, Mount Washington, Echo Park, Atwater Village), Westside design-forward mid-premium (Mar Vista, Culver City design-forward kitchens, Venice, Brentwood), Hollywood Hills architectural custom, and scattered Pasadena + San Marino + La Cañada premium. OC volume is lower but present in Newport Beach + Laguna Beach custom kitchens.</p>
  </div></section>

