    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Intelligent cycle sensor drift</h3><p>Sensor $260–$400. Common 5-7 year service.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Heating element + hard-water scale</h3><p>Element $280–$440. LA hard water accelerates scale.</p></div>
